<% can_front_balance = @invoice.sponsor.event.can_front_balance? %>

<p>
  Hi there,
</p>

<p>
  The funds from <%= link_to "a recently paid invoice to #{@invoice.sponsor.name}", @invoice %>
  <% if can_front_balance %>
    have transferred
    <% else %>
    are transferring
  <% end %>
  into <%= link_to @invoice.sponsor.event.name, @invoice.sponsor.event %> on Hack Club Bank.
</p>

<p>
  <% if can_front_balance %>
      The funds (<strong><%= render_money @invoice.item_amount %></strong>) are now available to spend.
  <% else %>
    The funds (<strong><%= render_money @invoice.item_amount %></strong>) will be available on approximately <strong><%= @invoice.payout.arrival_date.to_date %></strong>.
  <% end %>
  Please don't hesitate to reach out to us if you have any questions!
</p>

<p>
  Yours truly,<br/>
  The Hack Club Team
</p>
